WEBVTT

00:06:28.711 --> 00:06:30.904
Po možnosti z neomejeno
količino krušnih palčk.

00:06:30.904 --> 00:06:32.764
Tako je to s postmodernizmom.

00:06:32.788 --> 00:06:34.602
Tako je to s simboli.

00:06:34.908 --> 00:06:37.888
Preprosti so, poceni,

00:06:37.912 --> 00:06:40.417
ker namesto ustvarjanja prostorov,

00:06:40.441 --> 00:06:42.493
ustvarjamo spomine na prostore.

00:06:43.091 --> 00:06:45.947
Ker vem,
in vem, da tudi vsi vi veste,

00:06:45.971 --> 00:06:47.286
da to ni Toskana.

00:06:48.182 --> 00:06:49.327
To je Ohio.

00:06:49.452 --> 00:06:50.970
(smeh)

00:06:50.994 --> 00:06:52.819
Arhitekti postanejo frustrirani

00:06:52.843 --> 00:06:56.174
in začnemo potiskati nihalo
nazaj v drugo smer.

00:06:56.559 --> 00:06:58.786
V poznih osemdesetih
in zgodnjih devetdesetih

00:06:58.810 --> 00:07:02.058
začnemo eksperimentirati
s tako imenovanim dekonstruktivizmom.